AIP Brief

Files
--
Homepage Design File: assets/pages/homepage.png

Web Build
--
Use the latest SCSS compiler version of Bootstrap.
Use their components/framework as a base for all components, e.g. where we use tabs, or cards use the Bootstrap version and style them.
Create clean SCSS adding a custom scss file for our components
All components should work in any order if swapped, excluding the header and footer.
Use Bootstrap best practices

General Settings
--
Contant Container Width: 1280px
Elements backrounds should be full width while content is contained at Contant Container Width
Stats should have a  countup, e.g. $6.2bn+ the 6.2 should count up.
Cards should use the bootstrap block grid.
For images not supplied in Source Files, use a placeholder.


Source Files
--
Header Logo: assets/logo-header.svg
Footer Logo: assets/logo-footer.png


Font Settings
--
Font Source: Google Fonts
Font Family: Mulish
Nav font size: 16px / weight: 400
H1 Font Size: 56px / weight: 300 / line-height: 1.2 (desktop)
H2 Font Size: 48px / weight: 300 / line-height: 1.2 (desktop)
Body Font Size: 18px / weight: 400 / line-height: 1.5
Statistics Font Size: 70px / weight: 200 / line-height: 1.3 (desktop)
Tabs Title Font Size: 24px / weight: 400 / line-height: 1.4
Tabs Content Title Font Size: 40px / weight: 300 / line-height: 1.2
Tabs Content paragraphs Font Size: 16px / weight: 400 / line-height: 1.5
Strategic Partnerships & Control Investments cards Title Font Size: 24px / weight: 400 / line-height: 1.4
Strategic Partnerships & Control Investments cards Body Font Size:16px / weight: 400

Brand Colours
--
Aqua: #00D2E3 (e.g. Investor Login button background)
White: FFFFFF; (e.g. Text)
Neutral Darkest: #1A2332 (e.g. header background)
Neutral Dark: ##00D2E3 (e.g. header)
Lilac: #BABCC9 (e.g. Tabs inactive background)

